Returns the schema structure DynamoDB expects.

Example:

```
>>> index.schema()
{
    'IndexName': 'LastNameIndex',
    'KeySchema': [
        {
            'AttributeName': 'username',
            'KeyType': 'HASH',
        },
    ],
    'Projection': {
        'ProjectionType': 'KEYS_ONLY',
    }
}
```

